{"tid":1649910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"割乜撚嘢","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:01:21.000Z","uid":309617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4db0aa867a2cc9b50df4139e79532ab4bf92374c","tid":1649910,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"人哋狗隊打死手足 都未割<br />\n而家我哋因為一個生日蛋糕 就即刻割<br />\n屌咪分化啦<br />\n喺太子喺前線慶祝 係唔尊重當時環境 <br />\n呢樣大家都知<br />\n但係使唔使個個去曬推蛋糕post<br />\n聽日行動係咪唔使理？<br />\n熱門成版都係蛋糕post 好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚嬲呀 屌撚爆蛋糕佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畀我哋行先一步嘅手足 <br />\n只係見到我企起原地屌鳩個蛋糕咋<br />\n仲對唔對得住佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n自問p牌仔推唔喐<br />\n見住你哋仲喺度屌蛋糕<br />\n真係燉對家開心<br />\n對面依家睇到我哋弱點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大局當前 正經事行先 唔該</span></span><br />\n同路人 蛋糕撚 都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9bf026bcee0cbf63a6d43c98561dc0c3a24f72d","tid":1649910,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:29.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"03e6fdd16887b5e0b7c386cde3ec8cc379ddcde7","tid":1649910,"uid":135349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqSXdVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqSXdVR.jpg&h=5788bd60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23a93389b50c3444b5a3b6ca7080c672ce706355","tid":1649910,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"一陣2.00見<br />\n唔好喺度開革命模式屌蛋糕<br />\n做實事就冇人跟！<br />\n心鳩痛"}]}